        "title": "Open to All Teaching",
        "content": [
            "Learning for anyone should be a joy without many barriers. To fulfil this objective, IIT Hyderabad would like to extend its excellent technical education beyond the four walls of its classroom in select courses. These courses will be offered in online mode (Live Streaming) wherein working professionals, faculty members and students from various organisations, can attend the courses remotely, as long as the time table set by the instructor suits you.",
            "Important: These courses are not recorded classes but unique live streaming from classrooms of IITH for the courses being offered to regular IITH students. This provides an opportunity for the participants to interact directly with the course instructors in real time, which helps to make the lectures more dynamic, engaging, and highly interactive between the participant and the course instructors in real time."
        ]
    },
    {
        "title": "Registration Fee",
        "content": [
            "The fee will be Rs. 5,000/- plus GST per one credit. For example, for a 3-credit course, the fee will be Rs. 15,000/- plus GST. It may be noted that a 3-credit course typically has 42 lecture hours with 3 hours per week."
        ]
    },
    {
        "title": "Certificate",
        "content": [
            "A course completion certificate will be offered at the end of the course for only those who successfully complete the course. The certificate will indicate the name of the course, participant name, photograph and the score/grade secured in the course along with the number of credits.It will have the logo of IIT Hyderabad. Only the e-certificate will be made available. Hard copies will not be dispatched. Students who do not complete the course / leave it midway will not be awarded any certificate."
